      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## E1 — Flujo completo base (4G)\n**Stack:** Open5GS EPC + srsRAN 4G (ZMQ) · **Duración:** 10–15 min\n\n### Flujo (5 pasos)\n1. **Attach** — EPS Attach Request → Attach Accept\n2. **Bearer Setup** — Default EPS Bearer Establishment\n3. **Tráfico activo** — ping en loop sobre el UE\n4. **Bearer Release** — liberación del bearer\n5. **Detach** — UE-initiated EPS Detach\n\n**Prerrequisito:** `make core-4g-up && make services-up && make e1`\n\n**IMSI:** 001011234567895 · **APN:** internet",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.3.0",
      "title": "📖 Descripción",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": null,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 1
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "content": "## ✅ Condiciones de éxito\n\n| Métrica | Valor esperado | Momento |\n|---------|---------------|----------|\n| `mme_session` | 0→**1**→0 | attach / detach |\n| `bearers_active` | 0→**1**→0 | bearer setup / release |\n| `gtp2_sessions_active` | 0→**1**→0 | bearer setup / release |\n| `s5c_rx_createsession` | ↑1 | attach |\n| `s6a_rx_air` | ↑1 | autenticación |\n| `s6a_rx_ulr` | ↑1 | actualización ubicación |\n| `gx_rx_ccr` | ↑2 | attach (+1) + detach (+1) |\n\n⚠️ `mme_ue_count` NO baja a 0 en detach — comportamiento normal.\n⚠️ Contadores Gn siempre 0 en modo ZMQ.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.3.0",
      "title": "✅ Condiciones de éxito",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": null,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 1
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "content": "## 🔍 Qué observar en cada paso\n\n**Paso 1 — Attach:**\n↑ `mme_session` 0→1\n↑ `enb_ue` 0→1\nLogs MME: `Attach request` → `Attach complete`\n\n**Paso 2 — Bearer Setup:**\n↑ `bearers_active` 0→1\n↑ `gtp2_sessions_active` 0→1\n↑ `s5c_rx_createsession` → 1\n\n**Paso 3 — Tráfico activo:**\nTodos los gauges estables en 1\n\n**Paso 4 — Bearer Release:**\n↓ `bearers_active` 1→0\n↑ `gx_rx_ccr` → 2 (CCR-T)\n\n**Paso 5 — Detach:**\n↓ `mme_session` 1→0\n↓ `enb_ue` 1→0\nLogs MME: `Detach request` → `UE Context Release`",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.3.0",
      "title": "🔍 Qué observar",
      "type": "text"
    },
